article.description: — Nick Hopkins posted 19 points and eight rebounds as Siena beat Fairfield 69-62 on Sunday.
article.headline: Hopkins scores 19 to lead Siena over Fairfield 69-62
article.linkText: Hopkins scores 19 to lead Siena over Fairfield 69-62
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Nick Hopkins posted 19 points and eight rebounds as Siena beat Fairfield 69-62 on Sunday. Aidan Carpenter had 15 points for Siena (5-6, 2-1 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Jared Billups added 11 points. Jackson Stormo had 10 points. Anthony Gaines had 9 points and 10 rebounds. Jesus Cruz had 14 points for the Stags (8-7, 2-2), who have now lost four games in a row. Supreme Cook added 14 points and 11 rebounds. Taj Benning had 13 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
